  "body": "# Problem\n\nWhen signing transaction initiated and internet disconnected user can't exit signing screen. `Cancel` button is available but not functioning. After some time we will get timeout error but until this not grayed out `Cancel` is confusing.\n\n![Screenshot 2020-01-31 at 12 24 53](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5786310/73831902-c54ba600-480f-11ea-9838-7d7e27eb7ac1.png)\n\n## Steps to reproduce\n- initiate stickerpack purchasing\n- sign with the password and quickly turn off the internet\nYou will stay in signing screen with spinner running and non-functional `Cancel` button.\n\n## Implementation\n\nTBD\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\nTBD",
